@model ZLERP.Model.HR.V_HR_GZ_Salaries
@section HeaderSection{ 
    <script src="@Url.Content("~/Scripts/Views/HR/HR_GZ_Salaries.js")" type="text/javascript" language="javascript"> </script>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        var options = {
            HR_GZ_SalariesUrl: '@Url.Action("Find")',
            HR_GZ_SalariesItemUrl: '@Url.Action("Find", "HR_GZ_SalariesItem")',
            ComputeSalarUrl: '@Url.Action("ComputeSalar")',
            ComputeUrl: '@Url.Action("Compute", "HR_GZ_SalariesItem")',
            deptTreeUrl: '@Url.Action("FindTree", "Department")'
        };
        $(function () {
            HR_GZ_SalariesIndexInit(options);
        });
        $("#formula-tabs").tabs({ fx: {}, selected: 0 });
    </script>
}
 @*页面布局*@
<div id="Department" class="ztree" style="overflow: scroll;float: left; width: 12%">
</div>

<!-- 右边Grid -->
<div id="MyJqGrid" style="float: right; width: 87%">

<div id="formula-tabs">
    <ul>
        <li><a href="#MyJqGrid1" id="idinfo1">工资列表</a></li>
        <li><a href="#MyJqGrid2" id="idinfo2">工资细账</a></li> 
    </ul>
    <div id="MyJqGrid1"  class="mvcform" >
    </div>
    <div id="MyJqGrid2"  class="mvcform" >
    </div>
      
</div>  
</div>
 

<div id="HR_GZ_SalariesForm" class="mvcform" style="display: none;">
    @using (Html.BeginForm())
    {@Html.ValidationSummary()
        @Html.HiddenFor(m => m.HR_GZ_Salaries.ID )
        <table class="mvcform">
         <tr>  
             <td>
                 @Html.LabelFor(m => m.HR_GZ_Salaries.YearMonth)@Html.EditorFor(m => m.HR_GZ_Salaries.YearMonth)
            </td> 
        </tr>
          <tr>  
             <td>
                 @Html.LabelFor(m => m.HR_GZ_Salaries.SalarName)@Html.EditorFor(m => m.HR_GZ_Salaries.SalarName)
            </td>
        </tr>
  
       <tr> 
            <td>
                 @Html.LabelFor(m => m.HR_GZ_Salaries.AllMoney)@Html.TextBoxFor(m => m.HR_GZ_Salaries.AllMoney, new { readOnly = true, @class = "inputReadOnly" })
            </td>
        </tr>
          <tr> 
            <td>
                 @Html.LabelFor(m => m.HR_GZ_Salaries.IsSeal)@Html.EditorFor(m => m.HR_GZ_Salaries.IsSeal)
            </td>
        </tr> 
        </table>
    }
</div>
 
